Effective Date:               {PolicyEffectiveDate}

The Board Chair is the official spokesperson on behalf of the Corporation on matters relating to
policy and community leadership. The Executive Director is the official spokesperson on behalf
of the Corporation on operational matters. Depending on the nature of the community leadership
initiative, consideration will be given by the Chair and the Executive Director/CEO on delegating
this responsibility, as long as any statements made are consistent with Corporation policy and
practices.

Monitoring:                   This policy will be reviewed on or around {ReviewDate}.

